Text:
Works great on my Win 7 64-bit, thank you wallpapers and seeders!

1- Disconnect from internet before installing, starting and adding serial.

2- Block the program's updates in your Firewall:

Windows 64-bit path:

C:Program Files (x86)AxialisIconWorkshop
IconWorkshop.exe

Windows 32-bit path:

C:Program FilesAxialisIconWorkshopIconWorkshop.exe

Windows 64-bit path:

C > Program Files (x86) > Axialis > IconWorkshop > IconWorkshop.exe

Windows 32-bit path:

C > Program Files > Axialis > IconWorkshop > IconWorkshop.exe
